701581f-a.title: Bronx: Paulding Avenue - Waring Avenue
701581f-a.text:
Paulding Ave., at the S.E. corner of Waring Ave., showing old
farm sheds occupying that site. The view is from Astor Ave.
August 2, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
